- "I moved the layer from [960,540] to [1200,540]. I'll preview at start and end to confirm it moved rightward."
- "I changed fill color to red. One frame at that time is sufficient."
- "I added an ease-in on position from 1s-2s. I'll use range=[1,2], count=6 to see the velocity curve — frames should be closer together near the start."

